data.description: Now's your chance to move to the country! Built in 2008, this home sits on 4.5 acres, has 3 bedrooms & 2 baths. The property has a large lake, 40x80 shop with TWO double bay doors & a barn. The sale includes an adjoining investment property @ 555 Water Tower Ln. which has a 3 bedroom, 2 bath manufactured home on 60+/- acres. Lots of wooded area for hunting or just enjoying nature. Call today to own your little piece of paradise in Ohio County.
